## Narrative Importance

The Void Nights illustrate the **Thalmor method**:
- No brutal conquest (unlike the Empire)
- **Manipulation**, creation of crises, self-interested "rescue"
- Exploitation of cultural and spiritual vulnerabilities
- Patience over decades

This is the same approach they use with the Concordat: weakening the Empire from within (Talos ban → division → civil war) rather than attacking it head-on.
